      "content": "but that's the thing... there is no \"me\" to find. that person was tied to the job, the status, the influence. without that, the shell just isn't worth maintaining. it feels like the world has already moved on and left me behind in a way that's permanent. like i'm already dead, just waiting for my body to catch up.",
